title: Get Smart - The Complete Series (1995)
description:
Get Smart: The Complete Series (1995)

The Smarts Are Back in Control.

Max is back and control... and loving it!

Three-time Emmy Award-winner Don Adams and Barbara Feldon reprise their roles as Maxwell Smart and Agent 99, but this time they have a little help from their son and newly-minted spy, Zach (Andy Dick), and his brilliant, sexy partner Agent 66 (Elaine Hendrix). Max is now the Chief of CONTROL and 99 is now a Congresswoman in charge of CONTROL\&#039;s budget. Together, they must struggle to keep archrival KAOS from gaining world domination.

Episodes:
- Get Smart
- Casino Evil
- Goodbye Ms. Chip
- Shooting Up The Charts
- Passenger 99
- Wurst Enemies
- Liver Let Die 


Actors:
 - Don Adams
 - Elaine Hendrix
 - Barbara Feldon
 - Andy Dick

Video: NTSC Standard 1.33:1 Color 

Audio: 
ENGLISH: Dolby Digital Stereo 
SPANISH: Dolby Digital Stereo 
 
Subtitles: 
Spanish, French, Portuguese
